author: mpfingsthorn
msg: - Extended the AbstractCachingProcessingPipeline to synchronize access, i.e. if another thread is already generating new content for a specific cache key, the new thread will wait for the other and show the new cached result instead of computing it another time in parallel with the first.
- Extended the eventcache samples a little to test the above, also with a reader.
